      * Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   Parm                    FldNamXAr
     C                   Parm                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   Parm                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Subject to account charge - Ok
     C                   Parm                    DDCHINOk          1
